<document>
  <properties>
    <title>Subprojects</title>
  </properties>
  <body>
    <section name="Subprojects">

      <p>
       Aside the development of the main OpenEngSB infrastructure a number of
       subprojects were spawned. These projects focus on tailoring OpenEngSB to
       solve typical integration issues in a specific scenario.
      </p>

      <hr/>

      <div class="linkblock">
        <img src="images/opencit.png" alt="opencit"/>
        <div>
          <a href="http://opencit.openengsb.org"><b>OpenCIT</b></a><br />
          Efficient continuous integration server. Well-integrated into the
          OpenEngSB environment and used to build subprojects.
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="linkblock">
        <img src="images/openticket.png" alt="openticket"/>
        <div>
          <a href="http://openticket.openengsb.org"><b>OpenTicket</b></a><br />
          Issue tracker for iterative processes. Light-weight ticket
          management and reference documentation for integration.
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="linkblock">
        <img src="images/yaste.png" alt="yaste"/>
        <div>
          <a href="http://yaste.openengsb.org"><b>YASTE</b></a><br />
          Frontend for automated testing environment. Configuration and
          provisioning of virtual machines for testing.
        </div>
      </div>

    </section>
  </body>
</document>
